'Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Shipping list no.: 2009-0007-S. Includes source diagram and tidal information. Map no.22051. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
